'''達斯汀·蘭斯·布雷克'''（{{lang-en|Dustin Lance Black}}，{{bd|1974年|6月10日|catIdx=B}}）是一名美國[[編劇|編劇]]、[[導演|導演]]、[[電視製作人|電視]]和[[電影製作人|電影製作人]]以及[[LGBT權利運動|LGBT運動家]]。他以《[[自由大道_(電影)|自由大道]]》一作奪得[[第81屆奧斯卡金像獎|2008年奧斯卡金像獎]][[奧斯卡最佳原創劇本獎|最佳原創劇本]]。

==早年生活==
布雷克的父親勞爾·加里森（Raul Garrison）在布雷克年輕時就離開了他患有[[小兒麻痺症|骨髓灰質症]]的母親羅莎娜（Roseanna）<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/joshua-kors/oscar-in-hand-on-the-road_b_694527.html |title=Oscar Winner Dustin Lance Black on Mormonism, Prop 8, Sarah Palin and the Challenges of Being Gay |last=Kors |first=Joshua |date=2010-08-26 |work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]] |access-date=2017-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312055559/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/joshua-kors/oscar-in-hand-on-the-road_b_694527.html |archive-date=2017-03-12 |url-status=live  }}</ref>和他的兩個兄弟：馬庫斯·勞爾（Marcus Raul）和托德·布萊恩特（Todd Bryant）。他們在[[摩門教|摩門教]]家庭長大<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=4807 |title=Meet Mr. Black: Oscar-winning ''Milk'' screenwriter Dustin Lance Black refuses to settle for anything less than full LGBT equality.: Feature Story section: Metro Weekly magazine |publisher=Metroweekly.com |date=2010-01-21 |access-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021205130/http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=4807 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |url-status=live  }}</ref><ref name=ABus>{{cite magazine| title = Sex, guys, and videotape: "reality" filmmaker Dustin Lance Black talks about turning the camera on himself—and on five young gay men out for fun—in ''On the Bus''| date = June 25, 2002| magazine = [[The_Advocate_(LGBT_magazine)|The Advocate]]| first = Chuck| last = Kim}}</ref>，原本住在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]的[[聖安東尼奧|聖安東尼奧]]，後來搬家到[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的[[薩利納斯|薩利納斯]] <ref name=BAR>{{cite web| url = http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=462| title = How he got ''Milk''| access-date = 2008-07-24| date = 2008-02-21| publisher = [[Bay_Area_Reporter|Bay Area Reporter]] | first = David| last = Lamble| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110127063235/http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=462| archive-date = 2011-01-27| url-status = live}}</ref><ref name=Focus>{{cite web| url = http://www.filminfocus.com/film/milk/castncrew?member=dustin_lance_black| title = Cast & Crew: Dustin Lance Black| access-date = 2008-11-15| publisher = [[Focus_Features|Focus Features]]| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081207225848/http://www.filminfocus.com/film/milk/castncrew?member=dustin_lance_black| archive-date = 2008-12-07| url-status = dead}}</ref>。

因為在摩門教文化與[[軍事基地|軍事基地]]的圍繞中長大，所以布雷克曾經擔心他的性取向，六、七歲時他發現自己被一個鄰居男孩所吸引，他告訴自己：「我會下地獄的。如果我承認，我會受到傷害，我會被打倒。（I'm going to hell. And if I ever admit it, I'll be hurt, and I'll be brought down.）」<ref name=BAR/>。他說他對自己的性取向的「敏銳意識」使他變得陰暗、害羞，有時甚至有自殺念頭。他在大學四年級時出櫃<ref name=BAR/>。

在{{link-en|北薩利納斯中學|North Salinas High School}}就讀期間，他開始在薩利納斯的{{link-en|西部舞台|Hartnell College#The Western Stage}}劇院工作<ref name=BAR/>，後來在好萊塢哈德遜主舞台劇院（Hollywood's Hudson Main Stage Theater）從事包括《{{link-en|Bare|Bare}}》在內的製作工作<ref>{{cite magazine| url = https://www.variety.com/review/VE1117788465.html?categoryid=33&cs=1| title = Theater Review: ''Bare''| access-date = July 25, 2008| date = October 25, 2000| magazine = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]| first = Julio| last = Martinez| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080921083434/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117788465.html?categoryid=33&cs=1| archive-date = September 21, 2008| url-status = live| df = mdy-all}}</ref>。布萊克就讀於{{link-en|加利福尼亞大學洛杉磯分校戲劇、電影和電視學院|UCLA School of Theater, Film and Television}}同時向舞台導演學徒、從事表演工作並在劇院燈光團隊工作<ref name=Metro>{{cite web| url = http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=3815| title = ''Milk''-ing the Silver Screen| access-date = 2008-11-15| date = 2008-10-02| publisher = [[Metro_Weekly|Metro Weekly]] | first = Larry| last = Nichols| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110608205425/http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=3815| archive-date = 2011-06-08| url-status = live}}</ref>。他在1996年以優異成績畢業。

